Izina ryabaye ikimenyabose ni Claire[cyangwa Kerere], umukobwa wa Kankwanzi  na Bushombe bo mu Ikinamico Urunana, amazemo [[Umwaka|imyaka]] irenga cumi n’ibiri amazina ye nyakuri ni '''Umwali Aurore'''.

== Ubuzima ==
'''claire''' cyangwa '''Kerere''' Ubusanzwe yitwa '''Umwali Aurore''' akaba yaramamaye nka Claire mu [https://rw.scienceforming.com/10863495-what-is-drama ikinamico]<ref>https://www.bbc.com/gahuza/podcasts/p07yjfjq/p098qrz0</ref> urunana<ref>https://www.bbc.com/gahuza/podcasts/p07yjfjq/p0c54wg1</ref> yanyuraga kuri [https://www.bbc.com/ BBC] ,<ref>https://www.bbc.com/</ref> [[https://www.bbc.com/ British Broadcasting Corporation]],<ref>https://www.bbc.com/</ref> iri zina ni naryo abaturanyi bamuhamagara iwabo i [[Nyamirambo]] kuri 40. Yatangiye gukina Urunana<ref>https://www.bbc.com/gahuza/podcasts/p07yjfjq/p0c54wg1</ref> yiga mu kiburamwaka mu mwaka wa 2005.Icyo gihe ajya gukina Urunana<ref>https://podcasts.apple.com/gb/podcast/ikinamico-urunana/id1492479210</ref> ntiyari azi ibyo arimo neza nk’umwana wari umaze igihe gito atangiye kwiga kugenda no guca akenge. Yinjiye mu ikinamico ajyanwe n’[[Umubyeyi Sharifa|umubyeyi]] we [[Muhutukazi Marie Mediatrice]] [uwo bakinana nka Kankwanzi [<nowiki/>[[Muhutukazi Marie Mediatrice]]] ari na we  [[Umubyeyi Sharifa|umubyeyi]] we mu Runana]. Umwali Aurole, ubu yiga mu [[umwaka]] wa kane mu [[ishuri]] rya [https://vymaps.com/RW/St-Philip-Tvet-School-31529/ Saint Philippe Gikondo]<ref>http://hanga.rw/read_article.php?article=1789&art=Kigali:Umurenge%20wa%20Gikondo%20ukomeje%20.html</ref> riherereye m'Umurenge wa Kigarama mu [[Akarere ka Kicukiro|akarere ka kicukiro]], mu ishami ry’ibaruramari. Yavukiye mu [[umujyi wa Kigali]], i [[Nyamirambo]] aho ni mu [[akarere ka Nyarugenge]] ari naho [[Umwana|abana]] n’[[Umubyeyi Sharifa|umubyeyi]] we [[Muhutukazi Marie Mediatrice]] ['''Kankwanzi'''].<ref>https://www.eachamps.rw/article/5604/Shira-amatsiko-kuri-Kankwanzi-ukinana-numukobwa-we-mu-Runana</ref>

== Gukina Ikinamico ==


'''Umwali  Aurore''' w’imyaka 17 avuga ko atajya agorwa no gukina ari [[Umwana|umukobwa]]  wo mu cyaro, icyamufashije cyane ngo ni uko yatangiye kubikina akiri muto bityo abikuriramo bikiyongeraho ko yumva akunze [[Icyarabu|icyaro]].Ati “Uretse ko dukina ibyanditse ariko nubwo navukiye mu [[Kigali|umujyi wa Kigali]] [[ubuzima]] bw’icyaro ndabukunda, mu gukina ndabanza nkishyira mu buzima bw’icyaro nkabona gukina nk’[[umwana]] wo mu cyaro. Iyo Umwali na [[Nyinawamwiza Laetitia|nyina]] bari mu rugo mu buzima busanzwe ntiwapfa kumenya ko bakinana mu Runana<ref>https://www.bbc.com/gahuza/podcasts/p07yjfjq/p0c54wg1</ref> gusa hari [[Igiherero|igihe]] baterura ikiganiro ukumvamo amajwi yo kwa Bushombe na Kankwanzi ([[Muhutukazi Marie Mediatrice]]) i [[Nyamirambo]]. Umwali avuga ko kuba yarahawe gukina ari [[umwana]] wa Kankwanzi [<nowiki/>[[Muhutukazi Marie Mediatrice]]] ari na we nyina w’amaraso ngo “Bimfasha kwirekura mu gukina.”<ref>https://yegob.rw/ibiteye-amatsiko-wibaza-kuri-kankwanzi-wo-mu-runanaumubano-we-na-bushombe-icyo-apfana-na-claire/</ref>

=== Urunana ===
'''Umwali Aurore''' nka '''Kerere''' cyangwa '''Claire''' yibuka ko akinjira mu [https://rw.scienceforming.com/10863495-what-is-drama ikinamico]<ref>https://www.bbc.com/gahuza/podcasts/p07yjfjq/p098qrz0</ref> Urunana,<ref>https://podcasts.apple.com/gb/podcast/ikinamico-urunana/id1492479210</ref> amafaranga ya mbere bamuhembye nyina yamuguriyemo [http://ukwezi.rw/Imyidagaduro/article/VIDEO-Twaganiriye-na-Golizo-igipupe-gitangaje-kiganira-nk-abantu-bikayobera-benshi-i-Kigali?fbclid=IwAR3CGQB9epOB4ACxk346HDfEX9pGfj8rFe9cxf2MsazZkV9lgdIEO29IyJE igipupe], gusa amaze guca akenge ari we bacishaho amafaranga yabashije kwigurira [[:en:Telephone|telefone]] igezweho.Hejuru y’inyungu nyinshi yakuye mu Runana, '''Umwali Aurore''' avuga ko igikomeye yungutse [[Umuryango w’Abibumye|umuryango]] mushya ndetse ngo ni byo bimwishyurira [[ishuri]].Ati “Igikomeye nungukiye mu [https://rw.cultureoeuvre.com/10561828-what-is-theater ikinamico] Urunana ni uko hari inyigisho batanga ku rubyiruko nanjye ngafataho, harimo n’inyungu z’amafaranga, mbasha kwiyishyurira [[ishuri]] kubera gukina.”Umwali avuga ko i [[Nyamirambo]] ahafite inshuti z’urungano banafitanye umubano ukomeye hanze y’ikinamico<ref>https://rw.cultureoeuvre.com/10561828-what-is-theater</ref> nka Petero, Mutesi, Obama musaza we nabandi.<ref>http://isimbi.rw/imyidagaduro/article/menya-claire-umukobwa-wa-kankwanzi-mu-maraso-akaba-uwa-bushombe-mu-runana</ref>

== Inzozi ==
'''Umwali Aurore''' nka '''Kerere''' cyangwa '''Claire''' Inzozi afite harimo kwagura impano ye akazavamo [[Umuturirwa|umuntu]] ukomeye mu ikinamico.<ref>https://www.bbc.com/gahuza/podcasts/p07yjfjq/p098qrz0</ref> Ikindi gikomeye yifuza ni ukuzaba [[Ubucuruzi Mpuzamahanga bw’Ibinyabuzima Bwenda Gucika|umucuruzi]] uzwi mu '''[[Rwanda]]''' agakoresha ubumenyi yakuye mu [[ishuri]].Ati “Numva nacuruza ibintu byo [[Kuragira|kurya]], ngashinga nka alimentation<ref>https://fr.wikipedia.org/wiki/Alimentation</ref> cyangwa byazanshobokera ngashinga [[Hotel Rwanda|hoteli]].”<ref>http://isimbi.rw/imyidagaduro/article/menya-claire-umukobwa-wa-kankwanzi-mu-maraso-akaba-uwa-bushombe-mu-runana</ref>

